title: #119 - Sam Schacher & ME
description: Co-Host of HLN's On Call w/ Dr. Drew, Sam Schacher, hangs out in the Mancave w/ me & talks about her work on Judge Judy, On Call, The Rolling Stone Rape Debacle, the irony of her name, and we end with the weirdest prank phone call I've ever gotten in my life.
